<li id="cite_note-40"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-40">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text">Menzel, S. 124 – 125</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-41"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-41">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text">Menzel, S. 125</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-42">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text">Menzel, S. 126–127</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Stokke-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">↑ <sup><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-Stokke_43-0">a</a></sup> <sup><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-Stokke_43-1">b</a></sup></span> <span class="reference-text"><span id="Reference-Stokke-2005">Bård G Stokke, Møller, Anders Pape; Sæther, Bernt-Erik; Rheinwald, Goetz; Gutscher, Hans: <cite><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.bio.ntnu.no/svfelles/Stokke_et-al-Auk.pdf">Weather in the breeding area and during migration affects the demography of a small long-distance passerine migrant</a></cite>. In: <cite>The Auk</cite>. 122, Nr.&#160;2, April 2005, S.&#160;637–647.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-BTO_bird_facts-44"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">↑ <sup><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-BTO_bird_facts_44-0">a</a></sup> <sup><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-BTO_bird_facts_44-1">b</a></sup></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://blx1.bto.org/birdfacts/results/bob10010.htm">House Martin <i>Delichon urbicum</i> (Linnaeus, 1758)</a></cite>. In: <cite>Bird facts</cite>. British Trust for Ornithology. Abgerufen am 24.&#160;Januar 2008.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-45"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Delichon_urbicum#cite_ref-45">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.bto.org/psob/amberlist.htm">The population status of birds in the UK: Birds of Conservation Concern: 2002–2007</a></cite>. British Trust for Ornithology. Abgerufen am 28.&#160;Januar 2008.</span></li>
